name: Welcome to The Ambassador
description:
The Ambassador is a classy, old school club with a Jazz orchestra. The head conductor is sick and couldn't make it. As the stand in conductor, it's up to you to save the show.

Created by Cukia Kimani and Kevin Marais with help from

Brandon Bosch

Daniel Mendelowitz

Orrie Golombick

Laban Le Fleur

Game made during Global Game Jam 2017
